#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.betainc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.betainc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:1 of
msgid "Regularized incomplete beta function."
msgstr "正则化不完全 beta 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:3 of
msgid "Computes the regularized incomplete beta function, defined as [1]_:"
msgstr "计算正则化不完全 beta 函数，定义如下 [1]_:"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:5 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"I_x(a, b) = \\frac{\\Gamma(a+b)}{\\Gamma(a)\\Gamma(b)} \\int_0^x\n"
"t^{a-1}(1-t)^{b-1}dt,"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:10 of
msgid "for :math:`0 \\leq x \\leq 1`."
msgstr "其中 :math:`0 \\leq x \\leq 1`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:12 of
msgid ""
"This function is the cumulative distribution function for the beta "
"distribution; its range is [0, 1]."
msgstr "该函数是 beta 分布的累积分布函数；其取值范围为 [0, 1]。"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.betainc.rst
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:15
#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:17 of
msgid "Positive, real-valued parameters"
msgstr "正的实值参数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:19 of
msgid ""
"Real-valued such that :math:`0 \\leq x \\leq 1`, the upper limit of "
"integration"
msgstr "实数值，满足 :math:`0 \\leq x \\leq 1`，是积分上限"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:22 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "可选的输出数组，用于存储函数值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.betainc.rst
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:25 of
msgid "Value of the regularized incomplete beta function"
msgstr "正则化不完全 beta 函数的值"

#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.betainc.rst
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:30 of
msgid ":func:`beta`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:31 of
msgid "beta function"
msgstr "beta 函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:33 of
msgid ":func:`betaincinv`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:34 of
msgid "inverse of the regularized incomplete beta function"
msgstr "正则化不完全 beta 函数的反函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:36 of
msgid ":func:`betaincc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:37 of
msgid "complement of the regularized incomplete beta function"
msgstr "正则化不完全 beta 函数的补函数"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:39 of
msgid ":func:`scipy.stats.beta`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:40 of
msgid "beta distribution"
msgstr "beta 分布"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:43 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:44 of
msgid ""
"The term *regularized* in the name of this function refers to the scaling"
" of the function by the gamma function terms shown in the formula.  When "
"not qualified as *regularized*, the name *incomplete beta function* often"
" refers to just the integral expression, without the gamma terms.  One "
"can use the function `beta` from `scipy.special` to get this "
"\"nonregularized\" incomplete beta function by multiplying the result of "
"``betainc(a, b, x)`` by ``beta(a, b)``."
msgstr ""
"该函数名称中的 *正则化* 一词指的是该函数通过公式中的 gamma 函数项进行缩放"
"。如果不加 *正则化* 限定，*不完全 beta 函数* 通常仅指积分表达式本身，而不"
"包括 gamma 函数项。可以使用 `scipy.special` 中的 `beta` 函数，将 ``"
"betainc(a, b, x)`` 的结果乘以 ``beta(a, b)`` 来获得这种“非正则化”的不"
"完全 beta 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:53 of
msgid ""
"``betainc(a, b, x)`` is treated as a two parameter family of functions of"
" a single variable `x`, rather than as a function of three variables. "
"This impacts only the limiting cases ``a = 0``, ``b = 0``, ``a = inf``, "
"``b = inf``."
msgstr ""
"``betainc(a, b, x)`` 被视为单变量 `x` 的双参数函数族，而不是三变量的函数"
"。这仅影响极限情况 ``a = 0``, ``b = 0``, ``a = inf``, ``b = inf``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:58 of
msgid "In general"
msgstr "通常"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:60 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\lim_{(a, b) \\rightarrow (a_0, b_0)} \\mathrm{betainc}(a, b, x)"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:64 of
msgid ""
"is treated as a pointwise limit in ``x``. Thus for example, ``betainc(0, "
"b, 0)`` equals ``0`` for ``b > 0``, although it would be indeterminate "
"when considering the simultaneous limit ``(a, x) -> (0+, 0+)``."
msgstr ""
"被视为 ``x`` 的逐点极限。例如，``betainc(0, b, 0)`` 在 ``b > 0`` 时等于 `"
"`0``，尽管在考虑同时极限 ``(a, x) -> (0+, 0+)`` 时是未定式的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:68 of
msgid ""
"This function wraps the ``ibeta`` routine from the Boost Math C++ library"
" [2]_."
msgstr "该函数是对 Boost Math C++ 库中 ``ibeta`` 例程的封装 [2]_。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.betainc:71 of
msgid ""
"`betainc` has experimental support for Python Array API Standard "
"compatible backends in addition to NumPy. Please consider testing these "
"features by setting an environment variable ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` and "
"providing CuPy, PyTorch, JAX, or Dask arrays as array arguments. The "
"following combinations of backend and device (or other capability) are "
"supported."
msgstr ""
"`betainc` 除了支持 NumPy 外，还实验性地支持与 Python Array API 标准兼容的"
"后端。请考虑通过设置环境变量 ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` 并提供 CuPy、PyTorch、"
"JAX 或 Dask 数组作为参数来测试这些功能。支持以下后端与设备（或其他功能）"
"的组合。"

